package.name: Adyen_Payment
package.summary: Magento Plugin for Payment service provider Adyen
package.description:
Magento Plugin for Payment Service Provider Adyen. The integration guide for this Plugin is available on the Adyen Support website: support.adyen.com, type in 'Magento'
support@adyen.com
package.notes:
Features:
* Module name changes to Adyen_Payment * Cash supported as payment method for HPP * CSE Fix for onepage checkouts and IE8 * HPP payment method selection now automatically loaded from the selected skin.
